That's a bit different. Our normal military, except in the event of martial law or insurrection, cannot be mobilized against its people. Also, he has <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> extremely</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> limited powers as far as the military is concerned; I believe the president has the ability to deploy them for up to 10 days before asking Congress to declare war. <br>
